條及序言把尚未統一前的國家，區分為「自由地區」和「大陸地區」，「自由地區」係台澎金馬。</blockquote><br />\n但中華民國憲法領土範圍無包括台灣及澎湖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n金馬其實可唔可以唔要</blockquote><br />\n陳水扁年代已經撤軍 想放棄金馬</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n荒島黎<br />\n又守唔住又冇軍事價值"},{"pid":"c45e0d1737ea29f94279a94c7e65d906b62f0fc4","tid":416491,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:17:33.000Z","msg":"跟埋個先後次序 應該係中共搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c7dbf8d8b560d0f4b120a371f8c90abdcdddd9","tid":416491,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:18:05.000Z","msg":"強國講到咁把炮，做乜唔叫台灣上繳？<br />\n淨係軍政財獨立已放夠證明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10054164e216773574b3c019e968e07333862c4c","tid":416491,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:27:24.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解台灣會屬於支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03410b52f50e7d06757761e83be5d1b05654ff63","tid":416491,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都唔明點解台灣會屬於支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自古以來台灣除咗被大清國統治過外<br />\n仲有邊個中原朝代統治過台灣？<br />\n(除1949年後國民黨中華民國政府外)"},{"pid":"11e22946a38f925aeea8b413763a5e259f7cca17","tid":416491,"uid":29874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟埋個先後次序 應該係中共搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實台灣可以試下掉轉來玩，聲稱自己係主權國，支共試圖分裂政權，強烈要求支共將中國歸還或交返俾中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a18babcbdf484029ad213532fbc54ab7b5339c","tid":416491,"uid":56123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:22:55.000Z","msg":"根本就講緊事實，1949年前中華民國固然係一獨立國家，比共匪趕左去台灣後點會無啦啦滅亡左？只可以話中華民國領土得返台澎金馬，人地依然有人民，土地，政府，根本仲係到，係面積細左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff7d9f5e39fab64e982d170ba5664ebb2d291fa","tid":416491,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就講緊事實，1949年前中華民國固然係一獨立國家，比共匪趕左去台灣後點會無啦啦滅亡左？只可以話中華民國領土得返<del>台澎</del>金馬，人地依然有人民，土地，政府，根本仲係到，係面積細左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ca02215d90d6548b68baaa490d5ae2a11b419d23","tid":416491,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跟埋個先後次序 應該係中共搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實台灣可以試下掉轉來玩，聲稱自己係主權國，支共試圖分裂政權，強烈要求支共將中國歸還或交返俾中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪啫係漢賊不兩立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9adea5f3ea624dac22fc4489ef14578e319e22","tid":416491,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:33:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>跟埋個先後次序 應該係中共搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實台灣可以試下掉轉來玩，聲稱自己係主權國，支共試圖分裂政權，強烈要求支共將中國歸還或交返俾中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪啫係漢賊不兩立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講咁多廢話 支那過到台灣海峽到上岸先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ccfe14295c230fc75a20ac59e18a6773f07aa8","tid":416491,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T00:48:11.000Z","msg":"支狗最鍾意話人地永遠不可能獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好想有生之年見到蝗國各民族獨立建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=