 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb8ad2758ce662e7fa71ee5c6afb00a0b78710d","tid":416491,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但又有啲台灣人係咁嘈話佢地係「台灣」唔係「中華民國」喎<br />\n以前馬英九話中華民國本來就係獨立比人屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬英九係話大陸同蒙古都係中華民國"},{"pid":"08f58c3a5d4a16b5e0be786518a2e83fe43ebd70","tid":416491,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支狗最鍾意話人地永遠不可能獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好想有生之年見到蝗國各民族獨立建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國解體 各民族自決</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5a4edfcabe02a3b28004d90e6cab5c065c7530","tid":416491,"uid":37876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但又有啲台灣人係咁嘈話佢地係「台灣」唔係「中華民國」喎<br />\n以前馬英九話中華民國本來就係獨立比人屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬英九係話大陸同蒙古都係中華民國</blockquote><br />\n根本顏色對了就講咩都岩<br />\n馬英九或者國民黨人講就係賣台仆街，換轉係民進黨講就係正確無誤<br />\n<br />\n之前台北停電事件已經露出真面目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb62c4a19a1936beafc43d10ede967f8530c5e1","tid":416491,"uid":23874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都唔明點解台灣會屬於支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自古以來台灣除咗被大清國統治過外<br />\n仲有邊個中原朝代統治過台灣？<br />\n(除1949年後國民黨中華民國政府外)</blockquote><br />\n鄭氏家族嘅東寧王國奉明朝為正朔<br />\n算唔算中原朝代統治台灣？"},{"pid":"8fe8806ecf293983526389cb4c35adbe63b8eba5","tid":416491,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跟埋個先後次序 應該係中共搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實台灣可以試下掉轉來玩，聲稱自己係主權國，支共試圖分裂政權，強烈要求支共將中國歸還或交返俾中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係要埋個13億負資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036a15686acf209caa7c6225809272076212a1b7","tid":416491,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都唔明點解台灣會屬於支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自古以來台灣除咗被大清國統治過外<br />\n仲有邊個中原朝代統治過台灣？<br />\n(除1949年後國民黨中華民國政府外)</blockquote><br />\n鄭氏家族嘅東寧王國奉明朝為正朔<br />\n算唔算中原朝代統治台灣？</blockquote><br />\n當時明朝已亡<br />\n鄭成功管治地方只係以台南為主<br />\n唔係全個台灣<br />\n鄭成功係父係南方海盗<br />\n母親係日本人 係日本出世<br />\n幼年生活係日本 所以日本有鄭成功(廟)"},{"pid":"675bb51db96ab53f1d825a02bc6ce21dca04c8dd","tid":416491,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bdeff83af6a2399017938dfec81cda36c2eb82","tid":416491,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跟埋個先後次序 應該係中共搞獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實台灣可以試下掉轉來玩，聲稱自己係主權國，支共試圖分裂政權，強烈要求支共將中國歸還或交返俾中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實呢個正正就係所謂既兩岸現狀<br />\n即係一中各表<br />\n台獨反而係要放棄收回中國大陸, 台灣島建國"},{"pid":"55838efaabb3d15511ffbc4e611f6986ee2aa06b","tid":416491,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fdf8594ce9cf7e132a9b6559c835f46275a048","tid":416491,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquo